  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Match 3 game with a bit of mystery and adventure. Unravel the mystery and find the lost treasures of Montezuma. In \"The Treasures of Montezuma\", you do more than just find works of art from ancient times and activate powerful magic totems! You also follow the lovely and clever Dr. Emily Jones on her quest for the answer to a mystery that can change the world. Her journey begins in the mountains of Mexico, where she makes an amazing discovery that is sure to turn the world of archaeology upside down. But that is only the beginning of the challenges she faces...",
